Ranjish hi sahi dil hi dukhane k liye aa
aa phir mujhe chhod k jane k liye aa

Kuch to mere pindar-E-mohabbat ka bharam rakh 
tu bhi to kabhi mujhe manane k liye aa	

pehle se marasim na sahi phir bhi kabhi to
rasm-o-reh-e-duniya hi nibhane k liye aa

kis kis ko btaynge judai ka sabab
tu mujhse hfa h to manane k liye aa

ik umar se hu lizzate-e-girya se bhi mehrum
ai rahat-e-jan mujh ko rulane k liye aa

ab tak dil-e-khush-fahm ko tujh se hain umeede
ye akhiri sham bhi bhujane k liye aa
